{"tid":1750162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［立場咬住01］01編採人員發聲明話公司或違反選舉條例","createTime":"2019-11-24T09:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T11:58:05.000Z","uid":221265,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82d5843cc099c2f97e89144439229114509f3212","tid":1750162,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2647270018691935?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2647270018691935%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=8H50EXT8eKO%2B303r5eJ0KBR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=580787d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2647270018691935?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n精彩啦<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41xeLVB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41xeLVB.png&h=ad0594f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fb4b3982d2c363ef28640a7f39f15154ecf3710","tid":1750162,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉今日舉行，網媒《香港 01》昨日（23 日）以「評論編輯室」名義發表兩篇文章，列出兩張「不支持候選人名單」，一為「不符合出任區議員應有的品格和德行」，包括出選「中環」許智峯、「土瓜灣北」梁國雄、「田灣」袁嘉蔚、「海怡西」林浩波；另一張名單則斥「政治素人空降區選」，名單上候選人包括「城市花園」仇栩欣、「大學」任嘉兒、「鞍泰」鄭仲恒。<br />\n<br />\n一群《香港 01》編採人員今日發聲明，指「評論編輯室」並不反映他們的意見，認為上述名單沒有表明不支持名單候選人的原因，有欠公允，也可能違反選舉條例。"},{"pid":"013e428bb94db0a88c3de787d9d213f35bb6196d","tid":1750162,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad98ba1cbd5537510db1a7386093c91910d50cee","tid":1750162,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27c31019d1525d218feb06ac2bd497b9cbdbb7bb","tid":1750162,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-2